sentences: Jaspinder Narula (born 14 November 1970) is an Indian singer of playback, classical and Sufi music.

In 2021 she was selected by BJ Sam to represent India in the first universal Christmas music project with other global music icons including Hollywood Actor  Paul Raci, Swiss actress  Christina Zurbrügg,  Ghanaian Legendary singer  Diana Hopeson,
